sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Head as Head Pod<br/>6379, 10001, 8265
    participant Workers as Worker Pods
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Submitter as Submitter Job Pod
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Pod Lifecycle
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (informer)<br/>HTTP/2, TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create head pod, services, RBAC<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Head: Head pod scheduled & started
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create worker pods<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Workers: Worker pods scheduled
        Workers->>Head: GCS health check (init container)<br/>6379/TCP, None or mTLS
        Workers->>Head: Ray runtime connect<br/>6379, 10001/TCP, None or mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,Submitter: Flow 2: RayJob Submission (K8sJobMode)
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayJob<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (informer)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Note over Head,Workers: Cluster provisions (Flow 1)
        Operator->>Dashboard: Check cluster ready<br/>HTTP/8265, None
        Dashboard-->>Operator: Cluster status
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (submitter)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Submitter: Submitter pod started
        Submitter->>Dashboard: ray job submit<br/>HTTP/8265, None
        Dashboard-->>Submitter: Job ID
        Submitter->>Dashboard: ray job logs (poll)<br/>HTTP/8265, None
        Dashboard-->>Submitter: Job output & status
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,KRBP: Flow 3: Gateway API Authentication (RHOAI)
        User->>Gateway: Access Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS (cert-manager)
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (validate Bearer)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token valid + identity
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Authorized
        KRBP->>Dashboard: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265, localhost, None
        Dashboard-->>KRBP: Dashboard response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
        Gateway-->>User: Dashboard UI
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over Operator,Redis: Flow 4: GCS Fault Tolerance (optional)
        Head->>Redis: GCS data persistence<br/>6379/TCP, Redis protocol, Optional TLS
        Note over Head: Head pod restarts
        Head->>Redis: GCS data recovery<br/>6379/TCP
        Workers--xHead: Connection lost (600s timeout)
        Head-->>Workers: Reconnect after recovery
        Note over Operator,Redis: On cluster deletion:
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Redis cleanup Job
        K8sAPI-->>Submitter: Cleanup job runs
        Submitter->>Redis: DEL ray namespace data<br/>6379/TCP
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Remove finalizer
    end
